---
import { Picture } from "@astrojs/image/components";
import heroImage from "assets/hero.png";
import Link from "@components/ui/link.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
---

<main
  class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 place-items-center pt-16 pb-8 md:pt-12 md:pb-24">
  <div class="py-6 md:order-1 hidden md:block">
    <Picture
      src={heroImage}
      alt="Astronaut in the air"
      widths={[200, 400, 600]}
      aspectRatio="4:3"
      sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 620px"
      loading="eager"
      format="avif"
    />
  </div>
  <div>
    <h1
      class="text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl font-bold lg:tracking-tight xl:tracking-tighter">
     wenet UX
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg mt-4 text-slate-600 max-w-xl">
      As a UX (User Experience) designer, our goal is to create digital products and services that are intuitive, easy to use, and enjoyable for the user. We believe that good design should not only be aesthetically pleasing but should also solve real-world problems and improve people's lives.

Our approach to UX design is highly user-centric. We start by conducting extensive research to gain insights into the needs, behaviors, and preferences of the target audience. This research helps us to create user personas and user journeys that guide the design process and ensure that the end product meets the needs of the users.

We use a variety of design tools and techniques to create wireframes, prototypes, and mockups of the final product. These tools help us to test and refine the design, ensuring that it is both usable and desirable for the user.

In addition to our technical skills, we also have a deep understanding of human psychology and behavior. We use this knowledge to create designs that are not only functional but also emotionally engaging and compelling.

We work closely with stakeholders, including product managers, developers, and other designers, to ensure that the final product meets the needs of both the users and the business. Our goal is to create a seamless and enjoyable user experience that drives user engagement, satisfaction, and loyalty.

Overall, we are passionate about creating digital products and services that make a difference in people's lives. We believe that good design can have a profound impact on the way people interact with technology and can help to create a better, more user-friendly world.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
      <Link
        href="#"
        href="https://web3templates.com/templates/astroship-starter-website-template-for-astro"
        target="_blank"
        class="flex gap-1 items-center justify-center"
        rel="noopener">
        <Icon class="text-white w-5 h-5" name="bx:bxs-cloud-download" />

        Book for Coffee Chat
      </Link>
      <Link
        size="lg"
        style="outline"
        rel="noopener"
        href="https://github.com/surjithctly/astroship"
        class="flex gap-1 items-center justify-center"
        target="_blank">
        <Icon class="text-black w-4 h-4" name="bx:bxl-github" />
        GitHub Repo
      </Link>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
